    "name": "FaeTerra",
    "steam_appid": 3011470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/04d7b2998192e680527265e2dd093e83.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/751df25deb35e148103d1484c7ac55bd.poster.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/751df25deb35e148103d1484c7ac55bd.webm?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/751df25deb35e148103d1484c7ac55bd.mp4?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>FaeTerra</strong>, team building is all about strategy and creativity. Players collect and evolve powerful creatures—each with unique elements and abilities. Create satisfying combos with unlimited team mashups and dynamic evolutions, crafting the perfect lineup feels like discovering your own battle style in a  magical ecosystem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/e856d02c10b61c6ddd2770356398d99f.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/88342c599cf8d23345a729350a5f5350.poster.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/88342c599cf8d23345a729350a5f5350.webm?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/88342c599cf8d23345a729350a5f5350.mp4?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the <strong>Battle phase</strong> Faes will auto-battle against one another until no Faes remain on the field resulting in a win or a loss. Every creature has distinct <strong>abilities and evolutions</strong>, letting you craft endless team combinations and counter your rivals in tactical auto-battles. Discover hidden synergies, master elemental matchups, and build your dream team in a vibrant world where every creature tells a story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/52cb4d90ae6b40ceb7ad131f6de96c51.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/cbbeccb6ee8c538e051d2d21da0cc013.poster.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/cbbeccb6ee8c538e051d2d21da0cc013.webm?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/cbbeccb6ee8c538e051d2d21da0cc013.mp4?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FaeTerra</strong> is a fast-paced strategy game where you collect, evolve, and battle with over <strong>121 unique creatures</strong>, each belonging to powerful <strong>elemental factions</strong> like Air, Earth, Water, and Fire types. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/6cc78967087b919b162a8a9fe94848f1.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/bea56f14f3cb5fd3f09b9d6ed08eb8dc.poster.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/bea56f14f3cb5fd3f09b9d6ed08eb8dc.webm?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/bea56f14f3cb5fd3f09b9d6ed08eb8dc.mp4?t=1761795959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolve your Faes to unlock powerful new forms—each evolution is unique, Enhancing their abilities, appearance, and strategy in battle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/a351bc93cb0341f33a81242b1c933636.avif?t=1761795959\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras_big/a351bc93cb0341f33a81242b1c933636.avif?t=1761795959 width=800 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/08626b8fc7b9c97264b8d42bc5d3e1ef.avif?t=1761795959\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto battler: </strong>Battle your friends in PvP, manage your team, evolve, or compete in ranked matches!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Teambuilding: </strong>Offers unique strategies and combos to create the most powerful team. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deckbuilding:</strong> Allows you to hand craft your very own unique packs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Creature collecting:</strong> Master  121 unique Fae's with 13  elemental types.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras/0aa25ce0c8d34561914352112dc94c12.avif?t=1761795959\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011470/extras_big/0aa25ce0c8d34561914352112dc94c12.avif?t=1761795959 width=800 height=415 /></span></p>",
